msgstr "ຜູ້ຜະລິດໂລຫະ"

#. module: metal_fabricator
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:metal_fabricator.footer
msgid "MyCompany"
msgstr "ບໍລິສັດຂອງຂ້ອຍ"

#. module: metal_fabricator
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:metal_fabricator.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Odoo is entirely integrated into an App. Download it to <b>manage your "
"entire business from your phone</b>.<s><br/></s>"
msgstr ""
"Odoo ໄດ້ຖືກລວມເຂົ້າໃນແອັບພລິເຄຊັນຢ່າງສົມບູນ. ດາວໂຫລດມັນເພື່ອ <b>ຄຸ້ມຄອງທຸລະກິດທັງໝົດຂອງທ່ານຜ່ານໂທລ"
"ະສັບ</b>.<s><br/></s>"

#. module: metal_fabricator
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:metal_fabricator.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Of course, this is just an overview of the features included in this "
"package. Feel free to add new apps, delete/modify demo data, and test "
"everything around!"
msgstr ""
"ແນ່ນອນ, ນີ້ແມ່ນພຽງແຕ່ພາບລວມຂອງຟີເຈີທີ່ມີຢູ່ໃນແພັກເກັດນີ້. ທ່ານສາມາດເພີ່ມແອັບໃໝ່, ລຶບ ຫຼື ປ່ຽນແປງຂໍ້ມູນຕົວຢ່"
"າງ, ແລະ ທົດລອງໃຊ້ງານທຸກຢ່າງໄດ້ຕາມໃຈ!"

#. module: metal_fabricator
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:metal_fabricator.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"On the Manufacturing overview, the <b>\"Available\"</b> status for an order "
"will only turn green (labeled <b>MO Ready</b> in the filters) once all "
"required purchased items have been received in your stock and all sub-"
"assemblies have been produced. Otherwise, it will remain yellow (labeled "
"<b>MO Pending</b> in the filters)."
msgstr ""
"ໃນພາບລວມການຜະລິດ, ສະຖານະ <b>\"ພ້ອມໃຊ້ງານ\" (Available)</b> ຂອງໃບສັ່ງຈະປ່ຽນເປັນສີຂຽວ "
"(ສະແດງວ່າ <b>MO ພ້ອມແລ້ວ</b> ໃນຕົວແຍກ) ກໍຕໍ່ເມື່ອສິນຄ້າທີ່ສັ່ງຊື້ທັງໝົດຖືກຮັບເຂົ້າສາງ ແລະ ການປະກອບຍ່ອ"
"ຍທັງໝົດຖືກຜະລິດແລ້ວ. ຖ້າບໍ່ດັ່ງນັ້ນ, ມັນຈະຍັງເປັນສີເຫຼືອງ (ສະແດງວ່າ <b>MO ຄ້າງດຳເນີນການ</b> ໃນຕົວແຍ"
"ກ)."

#. module: metal_fabricator
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:metal_fabricator.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Once you understand their needs, <strong>generate a quotation</strong> from "
"the opportunity."
msgstr ""
"ເມື່ອທ່ານເຂົ້າໃຈຄວາມຕ້ອງການຂອງພວກເຂົາແລ້ວ, ໃຫ້ <strong>ສ້າງໃບສະເໜີລາຄາ</strong> ຈາກໂອກາດ"
"ນັ້ນ."

#. module: metal_fabricator
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:metal_fabricator.welcome_article_body
